    "Name": "Drillson Heavy Hover Tank",
    "UIName": "Drillson Heavy Hover Tank (Standard)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Drillson Heavy Hover Tank (Standard)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>10/17 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>215 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Drillson is a heavy hovertank that entered service with the Lyran Commonwealth's military in 3025. It is one of the best hover tanks of its type, and is known for its heavy armor and powerful armament.\n\nVery durable in combat, the Drillson can take part in the direct support of BattleMechs, using a Large Laser mounted alongside two SRM-2 racks supplied with one ton of ammunition. A single LRM-10 and two Machine Guns complete the weapons array.",
